title: Lincoln Boyhood National Memorial: Photo Gallery
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia     Photo Gallery              Photo Gallery                    Farm Animals   7 Photos  Photos of farm animals at the Lincoln Living Historical Farm.          Lincoln Living Historical Farm   8 Photos  The farm is a working pioneer homestead with a log cabin, outbuildings, split rail fences, livestock, gardens and field crops.          Hiking Trails   8 Photos  Walk the same ground as Abraham Lincoln did as a boy growing to a man.
